{"bangumi":{"date":"1991-09-27","platform":"OVA","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/a5/01/2047_t8Gzo.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/a5/01/2047_t8Gzo.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/a5/01/2047_t8Gzo.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/a5/01/2047_t8Gzo.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/a5/01/2047_t8Gzo.jpg"},"summary":"　　1982年，主人公久保健是一名普通的大学生。某日与高中友人田中的偶遇，给久保的生活带来很大的变化。田中是一位动画爱好者，他向久保介绍同人社团的伙伴。在他们的各种调教下，久保觉醒了御宅族趣味。\r\n　　1985年，久保和田中设立了手办模型公司“G.P”，业绩蒸蒸日上。后来，竞争对手控制了他们的企业。他们离开“G.P”后，重新振作又创立了动画制作公司“G.X”。终于在1999年实现梦想的“东京御宅族乐园”。 ","name":"おたくのビデオ","name_cn":"御宅族的录像带","tags":[{"name":"OVA","count":400,"total_cont":0},{"name":"GAINAX","count":388,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1991","count":218,"total_cont":0},{"name":"原创","count":180,"total_cont":0},{"name":"冈田斗司夫","count":177,"total_cont":0},{"name":"宅","count":77,"total_cont":0},{"name":"纪录片","count":77,"total_cont":0},{"name":"OTAKU的眼泪","count":69,"total_cont":0},{"name":"田中公平","count":48,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Otaku","count":38,"total_cont":0},{"name":"90年代","count":29,"total_cont":0},{"name":"もりたけし","count":25,"total_cont":0},{"name":"补旧番","count":16,"total_cont":0},{"name":"搞笑","count":15,"total_cont":0},{"name":"幻之神作","count":13,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1991年","count":8,"total_cont":0},{"name":"森健","count":8,"total_cont":0},{"name":"本田雄","count":7,"total_cont":0},{"name":"山賀博之","count":7,"total_cont":0},{"name":"山贺博之","count":7,"total_cont":0},{"name":"真人","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"访谈","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"樋口真嗣","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"岡田斗司夫","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"动画","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1990s","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"剧场版","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"园田健一","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"独立ova","count":3,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"key":"中文名","value":"御宅族的录像带"},{"key":"别名","value":[{"v":"OTAKU的录像带"},{"v":"宅的录像带